snippet.title: 'I was afraid he'd kill me:' Amber Heard takes to the witness box in Depp trial | ITV News
snippet.description:
Amber Heard today described how she feared her former husband Johnny Depp would kill her.

Giving evidence in Depp's High Court libel case against The Sun newspaper, she claimed the Hollywood star was repeatedly violent towards her. 

But under cross examination she denied being the aggressor -- or having a problem with her temper.

Juliet Bremner reports.
